Depends: walkr, grid, tidyverse, R (>= 3.1)
Imports: ggplot2, mltools, data.table
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Description: A package that facilitates the creation of characteristic-matched random portfolios. The package samples benchmark portfolios using two methods: Dikin walk and hit-and-run. 
